data.description: These sellers are motivated!! This fantastic home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Open living room, kitchen features an eat-in area, but also a formal dining room for when you're feeling a bit fancy. The primary suite is a generously sized bedroom with expansive bathroom. Downstairs, the 4th bedroom is currently a hair salon, but can easily be turned back into a regular bedroom. You'll also find a bonus living area. The in-ground pool makes you feel like you're on vacation all the time. Plus, the huge fenced yard is all about privacy and space to play. This home isn't just well-maintained; it's been cherished by its original owners. HVAC 1 year old, water heater brand new, pool pump/filter brand new, Brand New Roof! Sellers are offering a credit at closing to either buy your rate down, pay your closing costs, or for you to set aside for upgrades! Inquire for more info!
